attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles the rolling cart. First, he removes the four wheels. Then he unscrews the middle tray and the top tray to remove them. Next, he disassembles the bottom tray. Then he unscrews the sidebars from the base frame, separates the base frame, and at last unscrews the sidebars.
